attributes.title: DONT GIVE IT YOUR ADDRESS
attributes.review: I was scrolling through Facebook when I saw my wonderful president’s add for this app. I decided to download it because TRUMP 2020! When it finally finished downloading, I opened the app to a page that wanted my address. I felt so special for him to want my address. The second coming of Christ wants my address! So of course I give him my address, zip code and all. The next day I was going to get some of my healthy pea snacks when I saw something glint in my window. I turned on my outside lights and saw my hero standing outside my house. The orange man himself, Trumpie the demigod. I squeal in delight and rush out the door to see him. He turns around and in his hand is my dead dog Poppy. I asked him why he killed her and he said it was because she was black. Poppy was my pride and joy, my true child. I can never forgive Trumpie of that, whether or not my dog was black or white. -Karen
